## Development Commands

```bash
# Install dependencies (with dev dependencies)
uv sync

# Run tests
make test

# Run only unit tests (exclude E2E)
make e2e

# Lint
make lint

# Fix linting issues
make lint-fix

# Format code
make format

# Check formatting
make format-check

# Generate docs
make docs

# Generate OpenAPI client
make python-client
```
